 Upld Reward       : Time Given Per File Uploaded
 Sleep Time        : The time (in minutes) a user is allowed to be idle
                     (not doing anything) before MAX's kicks them off.
 Countdown         : The time the user is given after "Countdown" is
                     selected from the menu (when a user is online).
 Chat On           : Time User's Can Start Paging (Default Pager)
 Chat Off          : Time User's Have To Stop Paging (Default Pager)
 Max Pages         : Maximum Ammount Of Pages (Default Pager)
